title: S16 Ep91: Supernatural News/Parashare: Monsters & Motherships in Minnesota Edition

description:
Darkness Radio presents Supernatural News/ParaShare: Monsters & Motherships in Minnesota Edition!

Dave & Tim discuss a recent spate of UFO and Bigfoot sightings from their home state, Exorcisms, a strange Poltergeist attack caught on camera, a powerful Near Death Experience from an atheist AND your emails and real stories of the Paranormal.

Check out all the cool info on www.DarknessRadio.com
